com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class DoubleBufferSet<K,T extends DoubleBuffer<K>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.DoubleBufferSet<K,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type parameter
    T - the type parameter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeltaSet, DoubleBufferSet.Delegate, StateSet

    public abstract class DoubleBufferSet<K,T extends DoubleBuffer<K>>
extends Object
    A collection of DoubleBuffer objects being staged for particular layers. Provides indexing capabilities to reference the deltas based on physical references (to double[] objects) and based on logical referants (i.e. layers)
